1
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:21,760
♪Evening breeze cradles verdant hills♪

2
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:27,140
♪Embracing the waves of the deep sea♪

3
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:33,670
♪Paper kites aim for distant shores♪

4
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:37,400
♪Together, we conclude our tale♪

5
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:38,520
[Land of Dreams]

6
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:41,340
[Episode 23]

7
00:00:41,900 --> 00:00:42,740
Lidong.

8
00:00:48,810 --> 00:00:49,610
Qingming.

9
00:00:50,380 --> 00:00:53,100
Do you remember
when I first brought you here?

10
00:00:54,780 --> 00:00:56,100
I hope you haven't forgotten

11
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:57,740
about the rules.

12
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:01,500
Where are you going?

13
00:01:02,780 --> 00:01:03,980
Have you found the antidote?

14
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:05,980
Not yet.

15
00:01:06,740 --> 00:01:08,140
I will go.

16
00:01:26,780 --> 00:01:28,180
I want the antidote to the poison pill.

17
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:32,460
I have antidotes.

18
00:01:32,780 --> 00:01:35,260
But I have never heard
about the poison pill.

19
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:37,020
How about this?

20
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:39,180
Give me the best antidote you have.

21
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:53,340
What else do you want?

22
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:55,100
I don't want money.

23
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:57,940
But I want you to exchange it
with something.

24
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:00,300
All right. Go on.

25
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:05,780
I like using human blood to make pills.

26
00:02:30,580 --> 00:02:31,660
You are daft.

27
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:34,420
I have checked the ingredients.

28
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,820
It contains herbs
that remove feverish heat.

29
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:45,900
Where are you going?

30
00:02:47,340 --> 00:02:48,580
The witch doctor didn't lie.

31
00:02:48,780 --> 00:02:50,660
Herbs that remove feverish heat
can dilute the poison,

32
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:52,980
but not the poison pill.

33
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:55,020
I have already searched everywhere
I could.

34
00:02:55,340 --> 00:02:57,100
But I don't know much
about the poison pill you said.

35
00:02:57,220 --> 00:02:58,780
I can't find the right cure for it.

36
00:03:04,020 --> 00:03:04,300
Qingming!

37
00:03:06,340 --> 00:03:07,580
You better think this through.

38
00:03:08,220 --> 00:03:09,540
Are you sure
you want to give up everything you have

39
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:11,940
for this woman?

40
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:21,300
Brother!

41
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:25,000
♪Fate entwined♪

42
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:28,120
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

43
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:34,960
♪My sorrow overwhelmed.
I gaze at the moon, longing for you♪

44
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,410
♪Love as vast as stars♪

45
00:03:38,410 --> 00:03:39,380
♪In the galaxy,
I yearn for your presence♪

46
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:39,900
Brother!

47
00:03:41,740 --> 00:03:42,540
Stop.

48
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:48,380
♪In this fleeting dream,
love remains forever♪

49
00:03:48,380 --> 00:03:49,220
Zhou Yuan'an.

50
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:51,420
♪Without regrets♪

51
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:52,940
If anything happens to Xiaosheng today,

52
00:03:54,220 --> 00:03:55,540
you will never see

53
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:56,660
the other half of the jade pendants.

54
00:03:57,900 --> 00:03:59,060
Give us the antidote now.

55
00:04:06,380 --> 00:04:06,940
Wang Zhong.

56
00:04:07,380 --> 00:04:08,260
Give him the antidote.

57
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,340
Take them away

58
00:04:19,900 --> 00:04:20,700
and lock them up.

59
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,100
You wake up.

60
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:43,380
That was close.

61
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:46,340
I almost lost you.

62
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:50,500
No, I almost lost you.

63
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:12,420
Didn't I tell you

64
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,300
to protect yourself?

65
00:05:16,740 --> 00:05:17,540
This injury

66
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:18,900
is nothing.

67
00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:26,500
But

68
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:30,740
why is the Lin family's jade pendant
with you?

69
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:37,100
Back then, Zhou Yuan'an told me

70
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:39,060
Cao Fang

71
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:40,740
was the client.

72
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:42,540
He wanted to buy
the lives of the Lin family.

73
00:05:43,540 --> 00:05:45,420
He said
the Lin family poisoned the villagers.

74
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:47,500
As the coach of
the Blood Sacrifice Gang,

75
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:49,220
I went to the village to investigate

76
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:50,580
but found nothing there.

77
00:05:51,940 --> 00:05:53,380
So I went to the Lin's residence
afterward.

78
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,180
But the Lin family

79
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:58,620
was killed.

80
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:06,220
Yueniang...

81
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:06,900
Madam.

82
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:10,500
Yueniang...

83
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:18,620
Give this to Yueniang.

84
00:06:39,780 --> 00:06:42,180
Something wasn't right about this.

85
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,540
Jingzhe was killed

86
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:45,500
and Cao Fang disappeared.

87
00:06:46,050 --> 00:06:48,250
So I didn't pass the jade pendant

88
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,180
to Zhou Yuan'an.

89
00:06:49,820 --> 00:06:50,500
Luckily,

90
00:06:52,260 --> 00:06:53,300
the fate smiles on me.

91
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:55,380
I fulfilled your mother's

92
00:06:57,660 --> 00:06:58,900
last wish.

93
00:07:04,940 --> 00:07:05,500
Well,

94
00:07:06,340 --> 00:07:07,740
where is the other half
of the jade pendants?

95
00:07:10,220 --> 00:07:11,460
Do you really not know

96
00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:13,940
where it is?

97
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:20,620
♪Embracing the waves of the deep sea♪

98
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:23,140
Zhou Yuan'an is right about this.

99
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:24,340
Your father

100
00:07:24,900 --> 00:07:27,700
is a romantic literary man.

101
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:30,660
So,

102
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:32,300
where is the jade pendant?

103
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:34,820
I will tell you

104
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,980
after this.

105
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:41,180
♪Shielding the tiles from wind and rain♪

106
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,020
As for now,

107
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:45,940
we should come up with a plan
to deal with Zhou Yuan'an

108
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:48,100
and avenge the Lin family.

109
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:53,820
♪Swinging through autumn
to Stone Bridge Bay♪

110
00:07:57,100 --> 00:07:58,180
How about this?

111
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:20,980
Guyu, why did you take me here?

112
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:22,620
You want

113
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:25,340
the other half of the Lin family's
jade pendants, don't you?

114
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,060
What?

115
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:27,660
Are you saying the jade pendant is here?

116
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,620
I didn't expect that the jade pendant
I have been searching for a decade

117
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:38,340
would be in the old Lin's residence.

118
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:40,980
Tell me.

119
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:42,860
Where is it?

120
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:45,500
It's on the same spot

121
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,980
where you killed my parents.

122
00:09:12,380 --> 00:09:13,180
Well.

123
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,740
It's time to send you two
to your demise.

124
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:17,740
Hold on.

125
00:09:19,020 --> 00:09:19,820
Can you

126
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:20,860
help me

127
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:23,020
offer incense for my parents?

128
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:27,260
Of course.

129
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:29,740
The Lin family has been kind to me.

130
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:33,460
I should offer incense for them.

131
00:09:34,660 --> 00:09:35,140
Wang Zhong.

132
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:35,740
Yes.

133
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:16,580
It's done.

134
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:19,900
You may leave in peace now.

135
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:23,340
Zhou Yuan'an, don't come near me!

136
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:25,820
- Stay back!
- Stay back!

137
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,420
It wasn't me.

138
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:28,220
It was you.

139
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:28,900
Not me.

140
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:30,060
He asked me

141
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,420
to kill the entire Lin family!

142
00:10:31,420 --> 00:10:33,100
It was you. You!

143
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:35,060
Do you feel

144
00:10:35,060 --> 00:10:36,500
that your heart is burning now?

145
00:10:38,020 --> 00:10:39,780
Did you do something
to the incense sticks?

146
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:40,260
That's right.

147
00:10:44,170 --> 00:10:49,800
♪A glance seals our fate♪

148
00:10:50,830 --> 00:10:56,520
♪Without you, time fades into night♪

149
00:10:57,550 --> 00:11:03,110
♪My heart adrift,
seeking wings to break free♪

150
00:11:04,650 --> 00:11:09,510
♪Through tears, our love endures♪

151
00:11:10,150 --> 00:11:13,100
♪Fate entwined♪

152
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:15,850
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

153
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:18,730
♪My sorrow overwhelmed♪

154
00:11:18,730 --> 00:11:22,830
♪I gaze at the moon, longing for you♪

155
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:25,900
♪Love as vast as stars♪

156
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:30,190
♪In the galaxy,
I yearn for your presence♪

157
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:38,960
♪In this fleeting dream,
love remains forever without regrets♪
